%N A077406 In base 3: n sets a new record for the number of Reverse and Add! steps needed to reach a palindrome starting with n.
%C A077406 RECORDS transform of A077402. - Base-3 analog of A066144 (base 2), A075686 (base 4) and A065198 (base 10). Integers like 103, for which a palindrome is (presumably) never reached (cf. A077404), are of course disregarded. A077407 gives the corresponding records.
